Commission post!
I’ve been enjoying so much doing these commissions and I’m so happy for everyone who chooses me ! 
1 @diezperezsan this was a gift for the beautiful @rociio_shaun 
2 @phoebekate24 another gift for @haninthevan gosh I love so much everything in this commission I love her aesthetic 
3 @littlecloverhand  gosh u are so cute dear 
4 @griffon_gal súper cute commissions with her lovelies babies ♥️♥️😊♥️
5 @janelle.wilke this drawing was an oc that belongs to her! Thank u so much sweetheart for choosing me again 
6 @scandalousartist commissions number 2 and this time was oc from her!

My commission are currently close but if u want info of them u can check my commission account @kiki_is_fckng_mad 
I hope I have a wonderful week 
.
.
